    <p>EX­EC­U­TIVE</p>
    <p>If re­fine­ment, com­fort and value rank high on your list, then the Lexus ES250 (from $221,800) is the ride for you. It out­shines many lux­ury con­tenders in space, smooth­ness and de­sign yet is priced more com­pet­i­tively than any of them.</p>
    <p>Also, who says ex­ec­u­tive cars should be staid? The Kia Stinger (from $163,999 for the 2-litre) is a bruiser of a cruiser which sat­is­fies the need for per­for­mance as util­ity.</p>
    <p>The Straits Times Car of the Year 2018 also de­liv­ers a huge dol­lop of X-fac­tor miss­ing in so many cars th­ese days. The vari­ant to get is the 3.3-litre ($213,999, above).</p>

